{"tid":935483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦都肯認錯, 但飯民左膠就死不認錯","createTime":"2018-12-10T05:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T06:38:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21f93aa89bbd1a3ffe3b5aeb836c6ea0711c7e3a","tid":935483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"立法會淪陷, 主要係因為劉小麗、姚松炎、梁國雄同羅冠聰呢D被DQ議員.  <br />\n如果班死犯民左膠無係宣誓玩野, 中共就無藉口DQ議員, 改撚哂議事規則. <br />\n<br />\n見到梁天琦都有因此道歉, 仲話明宣誓玩野係「我們闖的禍、我們犯的錯」, 但被DQ既議員就從來無認錯.<br />\n<br />\n九西兩次選舉結果, 已經證明選民唔接受被DQ議員既白痴玩野行為.  劉小麗、姚松炎、梁國雄同羅冠聰呢D被DQ議員根本就係民主罪人, 唔向香港人跪地道歉, 一定無運行.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E4%BC%91%E6%AD%A2%E7%AC%A6-2-%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%98%AF%E8%AA%B0%E6%AE%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%86-%E7%8D%A8%E6%B4%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E7%25AC%25A6-2-%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AA%25B0%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E6%25B4%25BE%2F&d=5rMhux4GCg7QbMmwUwEGI54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=07d1e0fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E7%25AC%25A6-2-%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AA%25B0%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E6%25B4%25BE%2F&h=ab22b513\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E4%BC%91%E6%AD%A2%E7%AC%A6-2-%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%98%AF%E8%AA%B0%E6%AE%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%86-%E7%8D%A8%E6%B4%BE/</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦一再強調宣誓是「我們」闖的禍、「我們」犯的錯，強調自己在事件中有責任，即使他不知道梁游為何要如此宣誓。在《立場》訪問中，梁天琦迴避評論梁游當日的用詞對錯，只一再說，宣誓的方式，與他自己從政的理念有偏差。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦坦言感到失望。「感覺過往建立嘅嘢，而家全部化為烏有。」"},{"pid":"919bc7c27bb41f6dcf8d4b3774507487923fd202","tid":935483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161207/s00002/1481048686326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161207%2Fs00002%2F1481048686326&d=5rMhux4GCg7QbMmwUwEGI54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5fd50422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161207%2Fs00002%2F1481048686326&h=926c974f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161207/s00002/1481048686326</a><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦在選舉時把梁頌恆捧為「plan B」（後補方案），協助把梁頌恆送入議會，卻因宣誓風波，青政二人被褫奪議席。梁天琦認為「沒有所託非人」，但形容梁游在現階段就被取消資格「是一個失誤」。梁天琦承認「責任在自己身上」，說自己沒有留在議會工作，「我的責任是管理不善」。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦表示，宣誓只是釋法的近因，即使青政二人可以通過宣誓一關，若在議事堂上宣揚港獨，同樣會觸動中共底線，本土派終歸都會被打壓，「但目前是以一個最不理想的情况下發生」。"},{"pid":"6dfda115b0825fb7c7a9d1603d2decd53181243c","tid":935483,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:21:01.000Z","msg":"依家dq要理由架咩？"},{"pid":"67039d67a5dcd11601f8f71427e1a692665babf4","tid":935483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家dq要理由架咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宣誓玩野就係俾人有合法理由DQ, 只係以前無執正黎做<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦都已經認錯, 左膠支持者都唔好再死撐."}]}